{"tid":2386396,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"SmarTone 5G 網絡真係無華為設備？","createTime":"2021-01-29T14:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T06:03:15.000Z","uid":359622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac87e7a032528b75a3c4cacae3f5e7683891d0d","tid":2386396,"uid":359622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:06:45.000Z","msg":"原來只係 5G 基站唔係華為，背後連接基站網站嘅核心路由器係華為，咁咪即係一樣？即係間間電訊商都有用華為&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MAYjNQB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMAYjNQB.jpg&h=5ead72cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▸商家背景◂ SmarTone 5G 網絡真係無華為設備？<br />\n<br />\n因為 SmarTone 5G 無採用華為基站，所以心郁郁想轉台？咁就可能要望清楚：<br />\n<br />\n雖然新鴻基旗下嘅 SmarTone 係全港唯一冇採用華為 5G 基站嘅電訊商，但係咪真係整個網絡都冇華為設備？<br />\n<br />\n根據 2020 年 SmarTone 新聞稿&sup1; 指出，SmarTone 5G 採用香港寬頻網絡連接 5G 基站<br />\n<br />\n而根據 2017 年美通社報道&sup2;，香港寬頻網絡採用華為核心路由器 NE9000<br />\n<br />\n連接 5G 基站的香港寬頻網絡之核心路由器係華為，咁即係變相 SmarTone 5G 間接都係有用華為設備？<br />\n<br />\n而點解 SmarTone 唔用華為基站，實際原因可參考呢篇報道：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200530/RZNZSJ4QT3G3D57T2UR45VTLSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200530%2FRZNZSJ4QT3G3D57T2UR45VTLSQ%2F&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH6ha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=c7292bea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200530%2FRZNZSJ4QT3G3D57T2UR45VTLSQ%2F&h=e40450b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200530/RZNZSJ4QT3G3D57T2UR45VTLSQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n&sup1;&nbsp; SmarTone 新聞稿<a href=\"https://www.smartoneholdings.com/about/media_centre/press_release/press/2020/04/2020_04_01_429_chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smartoneholdings.com%2Fabout%2Fmedia_centre%2Fpress_release%2Fpress%2F2020%2F04%2F2020_04_01_429_chi.pdf&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH6ha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=204adb74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.smartoneholdings.com/about/media_centre/press_release/press/2020/04/2020_04_01_429_chi.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n&sup2; 美通社報道<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.prnasia.com/story/190623-2.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.prnasia.com%2Fstory%2F190623-2.shtml&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH6ha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=aa8633a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.prnasia.com/story/190623-2.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n#和你FC&nbsp; #商家背景 #SmarTone #數碼通 #5G #新鴻基 #Huawei #華為&nbsp;"},{"pid":"a31aec4fa2d03f31aeef296d7797d8cb286d251f","tid":2386396,"uid":20531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />smt係光纖租hkbn但5G唔關hkbn事架喎"},{"pid":"8329b3d333a2213c08589a9989f41d444cbe9c20","tid":2386396,"uid":246419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a31aec4fa2d03f31aeef296d7797d8cb286d251f","tid":2386396,"uid":20531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />smt係光纖租hkbn但5G唔關hkbn事架喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />5g要經光纖囉"},{"pid":"9eb69b5ae59774199787d1b04d67087e34bfb18f","tid":2386396,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"smt5g關咩hkbn  smt唔係租hkbn咩<br />\n你指5g天線內有蓞為？"},{"pid":"f7641ab15bba9232e944bd2136ddf4114035df4c","tid":2386396,"uid":271398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:29:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"410828d49ace6a3c5fcd9875ced3cec9fe25b086","tid":2386396,"uid":86224,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1